    parentName: "blockquote"
  }, "Vera hurls herself at the red dragon attempting to cut through his\nscaly hide. However, her attack roll fails to hit the dragon's Guard\nof 25. She chooses to inflict 3 damage, but the GM also gets a choice."), mdx("p", {
