    "id": "attract-attention"
  }, "Attract Attention"), mdx("p", null, "Cook\u2019s rifle is blazing as he mows down bandits one after another from his lookout on top of Hoss\u2019s General Store. He finally gets a clear shot on El Hombre, their leader, but his dice fail him. The GM allows the shot to hit for 3 damage, but it comes at a cost. Cook\u2019s position has been compromised, and the offended bandit leader sends five of his men to take to the roof of the General Store."), mdx("h5", {
